Now is the time of joy and gratitude.
As Euronews correspondent Carlos Marlaska notes, the film by Isaki Lakuestay organically fit into the collection of paintings that received Golden Shells, but the festival in San Sebastian was not without unexpected, sometimes shocking jury decisions, which are sometimes called the calling card of the competition.
